channel.title: This video game company took my username
channel.description: A stupid video game company made a game a few months after I started using this username. I'm not calling them stupid as in retarded, I'm calling them stupid as in idiots :| The name of the game is Ninja Shadow of Darkness, a.k.a. NinjaSoD. I used to be able to google my username and find just things about me, but now when I try, it's getting stuff about this game that I've never even seen before. I should get my username copyrighted =\
